There is a company out of England that makes a very close to original
curtains for early bay windows. I ordered a material sample and it is as
close as you are ever going to find. Not perfect, but close. Check them out
at:
http://www.vwcurtains.com/

Check out the Olive and Butter Patchwork fabric:
http://www.vwcurtains.com/fabrics/ob.php


